This work is derived from a pre-publication version of the manuscript _Formal
Geometry and Bordism Operations_, authored by Eric Peterson and published by
Cambridge University Press.  This version is provided for free download and
reference.  Reproduction in part or in whole requires the express permission of
Cambridge University Press.

The full version is available in both print and digital forms through the
